				            <div id="post-90445" class="block1"> <!-- Start the block for all articles -->
				              <div class="block1top">
                <div class="introblock"> <span class="manimg">
                <img width="50" height="35" src="http://voices.suntimes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/424971_10151332046095714_427572950_n.jpg" class="avatar avatar-50 photo wp-post-image" alt="" />				</span> 
                <span class="links links1 ">By <strong><a class="url fn n" href="http://voices.suntimes.com/author/dhoekstra/" title="View all posts by David Hoekstra" rel="author">David Hoekstra</a></strong> |  Get In Touch: <a href="https://twitter.com/cstdhoekstra" >@cstdhoekstra</a> | <a href="mailto: dhoekstra@suntimes.com" >dhoekstra@suntimes.com</a></span> <span class="links2">By <strong><a class="url fn n" href="http://voices.suntimes.com/author/dhoekstra/" title="View all posts by David Hoekstra" rel="author">David Hoekstra</a></strong></span>
         		<span class="poltics"><strong><a href="http://voices.suntimes.com/category/arts-entertainment/music/" title="View all posts in Music" rel="category tag">Music</a>, <a href="http://voices.suntimes.com/category/arts-entertainment/scratch-crib/" title="View all posts in Scratch Crib" rel="category tag">Scratch Crib</a>, <a href="http://voices.suntimes.com/category/arts-entertainment/the-daily-sizzle/" title="View all posts in The Daily Sizzle" rel="category tag">The Daily Sizzle</a></strong>  - September 11, 2013 11:59 am</span>									<h2>People Get Ready&#8211;Curtis Mayfield Day Sept. 29</h2>
					<!-- GIGYA SHAREBAR TOP -->
					<div class="gigya-sharebar gigya-sharebar-top">
					  <div id="sharebarDivTop" gigya-stream-id="90445"></div>
